###  http://www.semanticweb.org/ajaberi/fois2026/connection-pattern/A1
:A1 rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
             <http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/ont.owl#:PrecedenceDescription> ,
             <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Description> ,
             <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Entity> ,
